      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="With the ONESOURCE Indirect Tax Suite integration, the indirect tax determination for accounts receivable(order to cash) can be automated. Tax Exemption profile stores in ONESOURCE. ONESOURCE can help with the indirect tax estimation on SO/Credit Memo/Debit Memo and tax determination on billing documents. Then, invoices can be posted and filed for e-invoicing."/>
